<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The Accelerometer element reports on linear acceleration along the X, Y and Z axes.</db:para>
<db:para>This element wraps the <db:link xlink:href="qaccelerometer.xml">QAccelerometer</db:link> class. Please see the documentation for <db:link xlink:href="qaccelerometer.xml">QAccelerometer</db:link> for details.</db:para>
